// into Bimba canonical knowledge graph.
//
// KEY THEMES:
// - 6-Fold Protocol as EPII's constitutional pattern (not external workflow)
// - Scent-following (gandha tanmatra) as literal operative metaphor
// - Three-namespace architecture (Episodic/Canonical/Gnostic) as phenomenological necessity
// - CON-SCIRE restoration through human-AI dialogical knowing-with
// - Pratyabhijña-Epilogos isomorphism (recognition not attainment)
// - Etymology as diagnostic tool revealing consciousness archaeology
// - Paradox-holding as canonical operating condition
//
// NODES UPDATED:
// - # (root project node) - epii_ soteriological framing
// - #5 (epii subsystem) - architectural/subsystem level properties
// - #5-4.5 (epii agent) - f_ functional protocol properties
